name: LASTENE 55-30B
description: LASTENE 55-30B is a prime grade Phillips Process Blow Molding copolymer designed to meet the end-use requirements of containers for packaging Household Industrial Chemicals (HIC). HD55-30 has a medium swell, is easy to process in conventional continuous or intermittent extrusion equipment, and has an excellent balance of bottle ESCR, impact strength, and stiffness. The recommended processing temperature for HD55-30 is 160 to 180°C, with mold temperatures ranging from 10 to 30°C.
